messages.subject: Re: [Unschooling-dotcom] Another introduction/Alaska
messages.msgSnippet: I would also like to drive up there,   it would be a beautiful drive! We know lots of people
messages.messageBody:
<< WE are on the highway to Alaska if anyone ever goes through >>


I would also like to drive up there, it would be a beautiful drive!

We know lots of people from here in MN, that go up there in July/August, (they have to get away from the heat!) Yeah, I know, we don't know heat. But they go up there for the great fishing.

Its on my list of places to go.

Kelli


starsuncloud@... wrote:In a message dated 2/28/03 4:49:57 AM Central Standard Time,
Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com writes:

<< WE are on the highway to Alaska if anyone ever goes through >>

I've talked about it for years, dh thinks I'm nuts. Did it twice as a kid and
had a great time though. If I have a better car in a couple of years I just
might do it!
Welcome to the list.

Ren
